Location

Store traffic data is also available, Invent will receive that as well

Sales table

Process:

- Filter daily data as usable == 1
- Transform daily data to weekly: Group by  cluster_by (product_id, year) & week and sum sales quantity as sales_quantity, count row number as total_day
- Eliminate weeks less than min_day_in_week (4)
- Takeavg_ = sales_quantity / max(total_day, median(total_day))
- Manipulate avg_ column by taking sum(avg_)/ sum(1) for each cluster_by
- Assign clusters based on percentage shares [0.25, 0.50, 0.75, 0.90].
